body_html: @abdulwahabqurashi as Martin pointed out contrib ops doesn't work on Windows yet. TF is still built with CMake currently.TensorFlow built with Bazel will have support for most ops under contrib, but the Bazel build is still new, it will be enabled from TensorFlow 1.11. I'm working on a documentation for the Windows Bazel build. Hopefully it will help.
